headline.main: Waratahs Suffer Double Injury Blow Before Lions Clash
headline.print_headline: Waratahs Suffer Double Injury Blow Before Lions Clash

lead_paragraph: The New South Wales Waratahs' preparations for their Super Rugby clash against the Lions on Saturday have been thrown into disarray with late injuries to Wallabies scrumhalf Nick Phipps and lock Will Skelton.
